14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
15 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law not to be
16 codified in the Oklahoma Statutes reads as follows:
17 This act shall be known and may be cited as the “Food is
18 Medicine Act”.
19 SECTION 2. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
20 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 5009.7 of Title 63, unless there
21 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
22 A. The Oklahoma Health Care Authority shall seek any necessary
23 federal approval to provide coverage for nutrition supports under
24
